{"tid":309004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打同我一樣屋企都成個昆蟲王國咁？","createTime":"2017-07-04T15:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T16:21:35.000Z","uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc06c07f3571631e1e195586949ba7240baa384d","tid":309004,"uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"各位巴打養咗啲咩昆蟲係屋企？<br />\n我養咗螳螂 壁虎 蚊蚊 甲由 同 飛蛾<br />\n養到佢地肥肥白白 唔捨得走<br />\n見巴打們入到嚟 益下你地 附上寶貝寵物照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蚊蚊<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/234528_c34285ad148e18fc0606b8c140bb3bb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F234528_c34285ad148e18fc0606b8c140bb3bb5.jpg&h=1f1395c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n螳螂哥<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/234540_dc6255d4baf26a47e2975b715aecd537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F234540_dc6255d4baf26a47e2975b715aecd537.jpg&h=74d46aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛蛾<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/234554_69a7f9a45869ab6c5087db727cd7a919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F234554_69a7f9a45869ab6c5087db727cd7a919.jpg&h=1aaf70bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n強叔<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/234606_bd14d743b5e6678b4bfec15040cfa62e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F234606_bd14d743b5e6678b4bfec15040cfa62e.jpg&h=38ae0442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n𤩹虎<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/234618_abc307199b2b5288d0c4e64f1d998e62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F234618_abc307199b2b5288d0c4e64f1d998e62.jpg&h=72b24196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n介紹各位巴打用捉蟲利器 咁就可以養晒咁多隻寵物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/234629_eaecc89cc0ff10f57db3e2624e4c38a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F234629_eaecc89cc0ff10f57db3e2624e4c38a5.jpg&h=fb95e493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嚟緊要去日本培訓 見唔到佢地 唔知會唔會好掛住呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbfff40913e83083cd5c4dd8229dbfaa2d9f53b","tid":309004,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e24d12fd4b10d36c712464504b8f49dd6275a955","tid":309004,"uid":116899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"壁虎唔係昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過樓主點做到放個火機埋去隻壁虎都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地好細膽<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企有成竇壁虎都食唔曬啲昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9def74e6ce7510f8fa3a536830bca8baf5a2cd1","tid":309004,"uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壁虎唔係昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過樓主點做到放個火機埋去隻壁虎都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地好細膽<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企有成竇壁虎都食唔曬啲昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢地做朋友 當佢地係寵物就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇寶貝相睇啊？"},{"pid":"2ee2d1c8ff7c8ff8f981f3f357fe58c9da5069b9","tid":309004,"uid":116899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬係天生獵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細細個已經好鍾意佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過一行近佢地就加速逃走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張係屋企廁所影，佢係窗出面玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/vf45c102\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvf45c102&h=803b1c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw我家果啲好淺色，淺到見到啲內臟(好似係)<br />\n如果今晚見到再影"},{"pid":"b54b3c534cfcca32a4d15aa2b9ef672c53fb25bc","tid":309004,"uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬係天生獵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細細個已經好鍾意佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過一行近佢地就加速逃走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張係屋企廁所影，佢係窗出面玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/vf45c102\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvf45c102&h=803b1c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw我家果啲好淺色，淺到見到啲內臟(好似係)<br />\n如果今晚見到再影</blockquote><br />\n你要同佢多啲相處 比多啲蚊蚊佢食<br />\n我戈隻幾實色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef276a80e61c22f4be0e4717148e2a921aad73e","tid":309004,"uid":86275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"屌我好多強仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係撚咁放殺小強d野都冇用"},{"pid":"1c74ccb7e786cf0d6ead79702a200dab47b6cc22","tid":309004,"uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我好多強仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係撚咁放殺小強d野都冇用</blockquote><br />\n咁建議你用捉蟲利器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}